Package: aframe
Title: Create, Manage, and Use Data Analysis Frameworks
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Michael J.", "Kane",
    role = c("aut", "cph", "cre"),
    email = "michael.kane@yale.edu",
    comment = c(ORCID = "http://orcid.org/0000-0003-1899-6662")
    ))
Description: An `aframe` project follows the following priciples: 1. A project consists of a set of analyses.  2. An analysis consists of a set of components.  3. A component consists of R scripts and data in a directory.  4. R scripts in a component can depend on other scripts and data in the project but dependencies cannot be circular.
